title: 'Value for money'
body: 'DOMS stationery has really changed the scenario of good but low cost geometry instrument boxes for students in India. Kiddos to the founders of DOMS'

title: 'compass very loose'

title: 'Good but...'
body: @90/-. Apparently good make, colour too nice, but the pencil holder of the compass is detachable. It keeps on loosening and falling from the main body and us extrealy annoying. I glued the two portions. Now it's okay.

title: 'Worth it'
body: 'IF YOU ARE LOOKING FOR A GOOD GEOMETRY BOX WHICH IS AFFORDABLE YOU SHOULD DEFINITELY ORDER THIS DOMS GEOMMY'
